   OK-GRAVESTONES (Stroud, Okla.) _ When the good news finally came
to this tiny town grown accustomed to bad news, a collective exhale
of relief swept down Main Street. For a place left for dead,
perhaps it was fitting that the source of jubilation was the
arrival of a factory that would build gravestones. 1000 words.
