<HEADLINE>
IT MAY NOT FEEL TRUE, BUT GUNSHOT DEATHS ARE DOWN 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By DAVID JOHNSTON   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
