<SLUG> BC-R-CLINTON-SECONDCHANCES-REVIEW-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
TAKING SECOND CHANCES: PAR FOR CLINTON'S COURSE 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By DON VAN NATTA Jr.   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
