</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-CLINTON-SECONDCHANCES-REVIEW-2NDTAKE-NYT </SLUG>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) 
 WASHINGTON: golf score?  
<TEXT>
<P>
