<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-INEPT-LAWS-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
WHEN LAWS SHOOT THEMSELVES IN THE FOOT 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By DAVID E. ROSENBAUM   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Toward the end of every year, millions of Americans
