<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Consumer Q and A
 &HT;    (EDS: Moving on (a) General news and (l) Lifestyle categories.)
 &HT;    By Jane Greig
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
