</P>
<P>
   In the East or South
</P>
<P>
   On a rural campus
</P>
<P>
   On a residential campus
</P>
<P>
   On a campus with fraternities or sororities
</P>
<P>
   In a state with no anti-hazing law
</P>
<P>
   NOTE: Sports team hazing is more likely on a campus with
fraternities or sororities, but athletes who aren't in fraternities
or sororities are more likely to be hazed by teammates.
</P>
