<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-30 16:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4626 &Cx1f; sci-z
u a BC-SCI-WATCH-NYT &LR;      08-30 0680
