Rampant stealing, Khodorkovsky conceded, was certainly bad for
Russia. But, he quickly added, that is not his game _ it was the
game of the politicians. He spoke as investigators in the money
laundering investigation at the Bank of New York are examining
whether Khodorkovsky's bank moved funds illegally through the New
York institution. By Timothy L. O'Brien.
