broadband providers.
</P>
<P>
   In choosing thus far not to intervene in the budding broadband
market, Kennard says ``we are following advice as old as Western
civilization itself: First, do no harm _ a high-tech Hippocratic
Oath.''
</P>
<P>
   ENDIT
