   &UR; SPORTS (s) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   TEN-COLLINS-COLUMN (New York) _ By Bud Collins.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-ROYALS-REDSOX (Boston) _ By Gordon Edes.
</P>
