<P>
   FOR TUESDAY AMs
</P>
<P>
   Business Day Front Page (coded ``f'')
</P>
<P>
   (Lede story)
</P>
<P>
   CARREFOUR-PROMODES (London) _ Pressed into the defensive by
Wal-Mart's aggressive march into Europe, two of the biggest
supermarket operators in France announced a $16.6 billion
combination Monday intended to build a stockade against Wal-Mart's
ambitions. By Alan Cowell.
</P>
